Purpose:
Manages the connection between the laptop and the Pi, handles sending/receiving data.

Tasks:
1. Decide protocol: sockets (recommended) or Flask + HTTP
2. Set up connect_to_robot(host, port) function
3. Implement send_data(data) function to send movement/audio/video commands
4. (Optional) Implement receive_data() for acknowledgements/status
5. Handle reconnection logic if connection drops
6. Add config constants (e.g., default IP and port)

